response.overview: Seven scouts scramble up a steep grassy slope to an open building with sliding doors and a large brown table; Cristiano (shaggy curly brown hair, beaky nose, red cheeks) kneels and sucks the others; Erly (thick curly brown hair, right wristband) licks Cristiano's back while Cristiano sucks Fernando (short hair, large hoop earrings); Cristiano sucks Erly and the others: Ricardo (slim, muscular, short curly hair), Renato (dark tan, big chest, bald patch on left side of head), Bambam (tallest, beige cap, short straight hair frosted), Rodrigo (skinny, stick-out ears, long sideburns); Erly rims Antonio; on the brown table they top Cristiano in missionary position, and then from behind standing.
response.title: 2nd Eagle Patrol
